cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI

The paper deals with sound source localization, which is a problem in signal processing and machine learning. The use of manifold regularization and optimization frameworks suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of cs.SD (Sound), cs.SI (Signal Processing), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of semi-supervised learning, which falls under the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and the problem of source localization can be considered as a control problem, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SY (Systems and Control).
